CustomField.label: Add test monitor event count
CustomField.description: The number of times that a user on this team has added a test monitor. This number can be higher than the number of currently configured test monitors for the team if they've deleted jobs after creating them.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The number of times that a user on this team has added a test monitor. This number can be higher than the number of currently configured test monitors for the team if they've deleted jobs after creating them.
